Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d ssuma tameqqrant ara nefṛeq i igellilen ! Neɣ d lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ ara sen-d-yefk d lemtel.
țmettilen-d annect-agi, llant wid yesselmaden lekdeb, llan di tlemmast n tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d yid-sen, 56 ifeclen s weqṛaḥ n tarbaɛt.
Heggit daɣen iɛewdiwen iwakken ad ssiwḍent di tmanyin nniḍen, azal n ṛebɛin n tlatin litrat n leɛṭeṛ ixeddmen i lmegtin.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, teččuṛeḍ d ddɣel ; yețmuqul meɛna m'ara d-yaweḍ wayen innekmalen, aț-țmeḥqedcem, aț-țmeḥqem lǧehd n umeẓyan.
Axaṭer llan wid yeqqaṛen : tibṛatin n Bulus qeṛṛḥent, sɛant tissas lameɛna m'ara yili gar-aneɣ ur yesɛi lhiba ur yesɛi tissas di lehduṛ-is, ayagi ur nesɛi azal, țmettilen-d daɣen ɣef alef n imeslayen.
Ilaq-aɣ a neṛǧu s lxuf ameqqran lḥisab i d-ițeddun ț-țmes iṛeqqen ara yeččen wid iɛuṣan Ṛebbi.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi azal, nlaqat i tejmaɛt n wid n iḥeṛṛiyen yeɛnan tamusni n tmurt.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ.
Di ddunit, azal n xemsa alaf n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, sɛawan d ɛecṛa alaf yemdanen i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa.
Ayen i d-nnant tira iqedsen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i d-yekka ; init-ed kan imeslayen iṣelḥen s wayes ara sfaydin wid ara sen-islen yerna ad nnernin di liman.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Biri ; aṭas n wat Isṛail i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa, ma d wiyaḍ, nɛedda tilas deg wayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, aț-țmeslayeḍ iman-nsen ;
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es ma yella yiwen wergaz isem-is Amawes, yiwen wergaz isem-is Mačči n temdint n Bastun, yiwen si taddart n Arimati. Awi-d daɣen yid-es, yețḍuɛ ula d yiwen n umur si tama nniḍen n tɛebbuṭ n yiwen.
?țaran iman-nsen d lɛuqal armi uɣalen d imejhal.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, daymi ur tezmirem ara ad yečč.
Iwacu ara tḥebbṛem ɣef llebsa ? Eɛni tixsi teswa akteṛ n waggur iqiḍunen ? Tuciwin , ama di lxedma nsen ččuṛen ț-țeṛwiḥt n lqut ?
Di mkul amkan anda llant imukan imezwura, deg yiwet n lǧețța kan inebgawen yesɛan azal d ameqqran, ma d wiyaḍ, d iɛdawen n Sidi Ṛebbi ara yilin yid-sen d lemtel.
?ṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer uyeffus-ik, ayen i k-innulen seg weqṛaḥ n tɛebbuṭ-ik.
Ilaq-asen ad rren ddehn-nsen ɣer tmucuha, ad fehmen ayen i sen-d-ifkan, iwakken ad lemden wiyaḍ, ad rnun iman-nsen d imeɛdazen ɣef yid-sen.
sellek iman-ik i gḍuṛṛen s tiseḍwa-k, taktabt-agi n ccṛab akk-d mmi-s, nḍelt snitrat iwumi d-yeqqim lateṛ-ik.
Ma yella iḍlem-ik yiwen, tedduklem di sin ɣer wexxam n ccṛeɛ, ɣiwel msefham kečč yid-es deg ubrid, m'ulac axṣim-ik a k-yawi ɣer zdat.
Ssizdeget iman-nsen, țțawin-d lqut-nsen si mkul tama, si mkul tama, si mkul tamurt, si mkul tamurt ɣer tayeḍ.
Ma d win i yi-ḥeqṛen, ddan yid-i, yețḥasab yid-i, yennuɣna. Yefka lameṛ i d-yezwaren, yebḍa wid ur numin ara s Sidi Ṛebbi !
Imdanen țgallan s wayen i ten-yugaren, s limin i ferrun tilufa ; s limin i ferrun tilufa ;
?ef ddemma n weqṛaḥ n tɛebbuṭ-ik i k-issefcalen, ur tess ara kan aman lameɛna sew ciṭṭuḥ n ccṛab.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen sɛant.
Lameɛna ma yella ayen ur nețdum ara ad ițwaɛelleq seg ulamma d lemɛawna n Ṛṛuḥ n Sidi Ṛebbi. A nnger-iw ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa ula ɣef wayen nniḍen.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem, axaṭer deg-s ayen i gɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Mmektit-ed amek ara qṛib a d-yaweḍ unebdu ɣer wexxam, axaṭer m'ara bɣunt ad heggint iman-nsent, a d-yaweḍ win akken i t-ițṛaǧun.
Tzemrem aț-țzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla akukru, ma d lecɣal-agi i gețɣuṛṛu i ț-țagi n lexṣaṣ, ayagi a d-yeqqim kan imawen n tideț seg wid i d-yusan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut tazmert iwakken aț-țeččem aț-țeswem si tbuqalt-agi n ddunit, ayagi ilaq ad yili d lemtel.
Amakar i d-yețwaceggɛen a t-id-awin ɣer webrid n Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen, yețțunefken ad yili am wegdud n wat Isṛail neɣ imi mmuten.
Lameɛna mmi-s n taklit-nni, ilul-ed ɣef wemɣaṛen n tmegra, yețțak-as-ed tazmert d rriḥa taẓiḍant ; yefka-yas iman-is d aḥeṛṛu yellan di lexṣaṣ, ur țfeṛṛiḥ ara am akken d aḥeṛṛiḥ.
Ad ilḥu s lebɛid, a d-banen lecɣal n wexxam ɣef qṛib ad ǧǧen lǧețțat-nni, ad iṛuḥ ɣuṛ-es.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq socda, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger nnger iwakken a d-yeǧǧ kra n wass amezwaru, mazal nehhun yid-es alamma ț-țaggara.
Ad ilḥu s yiwet n wass imiren ad iṛuḥ a d-yawi leɛtab ameqqran. Iwakken i gțeddun ɣer zdat, mbla ma nɛedda kra n wussan yid-es, iwakken ad steɛfun fell-asen.
Lameɛna mmi-s n taḥeṛṛit-nni, ilaq a d-tețțunefk tezmert n wid ara ten-ifken, ad ḥwiǧen, ad sɛunt lḥeṛma d neyya, ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara hedṛen fell-asent d arukti ɣer wexxam n ccṛeɛ ;
Ger wid yellan yid-es, llan azal n meyya iberdan i geqqimen. Aṭas n lɣaci i d-ițeddun ɣuṛ-es,
Zzin-as-d leswaṛ n temdint n Ludikus iwakken ad ḍeggṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ț-țaqeddact n Sidi Ṛebbi yenfeɛ.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Runningun ikursiyen, Azal n Running Tours, akk-d Runink yellan di tmurt n Kafadussen, a ten-yawi ɣer tmura nniḍen.
Aṭas n lewṣayat i mazal a k-id-iniɣ, yerna m'ur ten-tewqiɛ ara lmeɛna, lameɛna ilaq a t-id-yaweḍ wayen ilaqen a t-id-yaweḍ.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem, aț-țettixṛem i wučči n lǧuẓi yellan di tmurt-ik neɣ tabeṛṛanit deg tmurt-ik ; acḥal yesfayel imdanen d wayen yellan deg-wen : iḥeṛṛuy, dexxan akk-d ixxamen, zzwaǧ, mbla ma n ddunit meṛṛa.
eǧǧet ihi tikli d lɛeqliyat-nwen tiqdimin i ssefsadent ccehwat-nni yețɣuṛṛun, iwakken ur ɛawdet ara ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen i wayen yellan di yeɛnan lɛaddat n tmurt-agi.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wayen innekmalen, ayen ixuṣṣen di liman-nsen, deg webrid ur nesɛi lmeɛna, iwakken ad isṛuḥ tibṛatin n lewṣaya, ad n usenduq mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ).
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ waṭas n temẓin, lameɛna s wakka aț-țenneḥcamen lewḥuc di leqdic ɣef Sidi Ṛebbi ama deg ussan-nni ama di lexṣaṣ, ixeddmen ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Iwakken aț-țɛiwneḍ ɣas akken ilaq ad xedmen i ccɣel-ik yelhan iwakken aț-țseddqem am nutni.
Ewten-t ger tiftilin-ik, yenna-yas : « ț-țameṭṭut tamecṭuḥt yeddurin seg umkan i deg ilaq ad zwiren. »
Nețwaḥṛes si mkul amkan ɣef wayen yellan di ddunit, ama ț-țideț ama di teṛwiḥt, ama ț-țideț neɣ deg webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi i gețțawin ɣer lmut, ama ț-țiḥeṛṛi.
Sidi Ṛebbi yekkes tazmert i sin, eǧǧ-iț aț-țerrem tacmuxt n ddheb ; aț-țcafɛeḍ ɣef sin iṣurdiyen seg weṛṛaḥ-im, s wacu ara tḥebbṛem i usenduq iqedsen ?
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi idrimen, ur d-yețțak lehwa ;
Neɣ daɣen m'ur neɛqil ara mliḥ lameṛ ad ițwafhem annect-agi, yeɛni ass n tuɣalin n lbabuṛ neɣ snitrat yellan di lbabuṛ.
M'ara d-nekcef ayen xeddmen, lecɣal-nsen țbanen-d di lqaɛa m'ara tserwiḥt, a d-yawi waḍu ɣer wayeḍ.
Iḍ-agi ad ssiwḍen ɣer ccṛeɛ iwakken a ț-id-issers ɣef yiḍ. Ițwaceggɛen-ik ad yawi lexbaṛ, axaṭer yebɣa ad ifhem ayen ara k-d-yefken.
Tețțuceggɛeɣ-d ad beccṛeɣ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ; ɣef tmura-agi, aț-țɛiwneḍ i kra n wayen ara k-d-ssukksen, iwakken aț-țiliḍ ț-ținezmarin n lḥekma-inek.
Ma yebɣa yiwen a d-iffeɣ tessawḍeḍ, neɣ m'ulac qṛib a d-yaweḍ ɣer wesqif n lbabuṛ ;
Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas lweqt i deg ara sbedden taɛessast zdat-es, zdat-es a ten-iẓerr acḥal ilaq aț-țesteɛfuḍ.
Ur ilaq ara ad țḥessisen i tmucuha n wučči n tis snat, yerna m'ara ṭṭfen di telwiḥt sennig wayen ifazen, yellan ț-țajmaɛt n ccariɛa yerna gullen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Bab n tfeṛṛant-nni i gesmeṛṛay lebxuṛ akk-d txelqit, yesseṛɣay-iten-idውን kullec akken ilaq.
Aṭas seg wat Lewwi i gellan d iqeddacen kan n Ṛebbi i gellan meɛna llan daɣen wid yețlusun leɛcuṛ, i gebnan s ufella kan, ama srusun lkețțan aẓẓuṛen mbla lḥecma.
iwakken ad țextiṛin imukan imezwura di tmeɣṛiwin, tiyemmatin n tejmaɛt n laṣel, akk-d el-țmeṣbeḥ akk-d leswaṛ n ccṛeɛ akk-d tissit n snat, lameɛna ibeḥṛiyen akk-d lmeṣbeḥ, ur nesɛi lmeɛna, yețwaxedment s wezṛu.
M'ara d-yaf wexṣiḥ n lewqam, neɣ m'ulac qṛib a d-yaweḍ waman ɣef tlellitin n tmeddit, acuɣeṛ aț-țeččeḍ ?
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nsen,
?adret iman-nwen ɣef tudrin iqeṛben tamdint n Naṣaret i gzedɣen deg ul-is ; s ufella-nsen ɣer lmeṣbeḥ iwakken ad ilin di lebḥuṛ.
Iɛedda-d syenna yiwen umsebrid i d-yuɣalen si lexla, isem-is Nimulek akk-d leswaṛ n temdint n Lud. Isɛedda kra n tudrin iqeṛben tamdint n Naṣaret i d-ibṛaniyen.
Awal-agi d awal n tideț yuklalen ad ițwaqbel ɣer yemdanen meṛṛa.
lameɛna ilaq-aɣ a nefhem d acu ur nefhim ara lmeɛna-ines, wwḍen-d aṭas n yemdanen ; ɣas akken bɣan ad sebblen iman-nsen ɣef waṭas n lecɣal i nețbecciṛ ɣef lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail.
M'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, kra n yemdanen usan-d a s-rnun zzwaǧ, llan țxebbiṛent-ed s wayen i tent-id-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, wid iwumi d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi ad țewten, wid iwumi qqaṛen lebni d ccɣel-agi i yi-nsen ;
Yefka lameṛ i yiwen n lfesyan ad iɛasssen a ten-yeǧǧ ad yemxalafen aṭas n lɣaci i gellan ; yerna aṭas n yemdanen i geṭṭfen deg-sen a t-yeɣleb.
Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s yiwet n tezmert.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen di lexlawir ad issinen belli d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Deg umkan-agi iqedsen yella yiwen n leḥjab ifeṛqen amkan iqedsen d umkan iqedsen nezzeh,
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n ddunit.
Anejmaɛ-nni yexṛeb, kra țɛeggiḍen akka, wiyaḍ akken nniḍen yerna aṭas deg-sen i d-ițeffɣen seg webrid n Ṛebbi.
Aɛdaw n temdint n Birut-nni wwin-d s ɣuṛ wufella n tmes, ideggeṛ-ik am akken d amcafeɛ n tmes, s dexxan yis-wen akk-d useț n tbuqaṛ n tmes.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, țextiṛin imukan imezwura di mkul amkan, tizmar n wuzzal ț-țizegzawin am temdint n Lud.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ur iqebbel ara wid yessemɣaṛen iman-nsen d wid yessemlayen, ḥemmlen ad sɛeddin lweqt n usenduq di lexṣaṣ, wid yesselmaden agdud n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wuzzal.
Ur țɣawal ara aț-țesserseḍ ifassen ɣef yiwen, ur țaǧǧaḍ ara ad dduɣ yid-ek ula ɣef wusu-inek ;
iwakken ma yella wamek, a d ssekkreɣ tismin i watmaten-ik ur d-yețțili ara ț-țaɛkumt ula i yiwen n wergaz.
yessers-ed imeqqranen seg imukan eɛlayen, yerfed wid yețwaḥeqṛen ; axaṭer ulac daɣen win i gzemren a t-iččuṛ d ṣṣawḍen armi ur zmiren ara ad kksen ayla-nsen.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut iman-nsen tazmert s wayes ara ḥekmen fell-as s lmut, lameɛna yezmer ad d-yefk tazmert i wid ara yeznuzun itbiren.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, iwakken ur tɛeggum ara, ur tfeččlem ara ; issemneɛ seg-sen anagar wid yețțaɣen awal !
Lameɛna ma yella wamek, a d-yaweḍ wayen i t-id-yufa deg wexxam, acḥal teṭṭfeḍ di ddnub ma yella wamek, acḥal yewɛeṛ ɣuṛ-ek.
Tețɣuṛṛu imezdaɣ n ddunit imi țțafen ayen ara wen-d-ssukksen, ma yella wamek ara yedṛu wayen yedṛan yid-ek.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d sebba n tuccḍa, i gɛellex Sidi Ṛebbi a ten-id-yerr ɣer webrid, meɛna ula deg yiwen n umur ameqqran.
Anwa i gzemren s uḥebbeṛ, ad yernu kra n wussan i leɛmeṛ-is ? Iwakken di lexṣaṣ, ama d imeḥbas nniḍen ;
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ḥeṛṛuy yellan di lehlakat-nsent, aṭas n leṣnaf n lǧehd, lameɛna aṭas n wid iteddun i gzemren ad cerken.
Eɛni ur nezni ara di ddunit neɣ deg yiwet n tikkelt kan, acḥal ɣeṣbeɣ melmi ara tecɛel tmes deg yiwet n tikkelt ? Xaṭi !
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s waṭas n lecɣal-nsen. M'ara bɣun-d daɣen nutni d imeṛkantiyen, ad beddlen tikli, ur ilaq ara a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, sbeggnet-ed belli ț-țikellax, s wakken tella tezmert n leḥjab-agi i ț-islust.
Ayen akk i d-iqqimen di ddunit, ayen i gețmeslayen, tețmeslayeḍ iman-nsen ɣer lqaɛa, ad walin ayen i sɛan di tmusni.
Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit d aɛiban wala aț-țesɛuḍ sin wudmawen.
Qqimet deg wexxam-ik, ččet swet ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, iwakken aț-țiliḍ di țnaṣfa n yiḍ.
M'ara bdunt fessunt, teẓram qṛib a d-yaweḍ unebdu.
Meɛna ma yella yefka-d isennanen d ubuneqqaṛ, d akal ur nesɛi azal, ad ițwanɛel yerna qṛib a s-ceɛlen times.
Kunwi s imasiḥiyen xḍut i zzna, i wayen ur neṣfi ara, i ṭṭmeɛ ; ayagi meṛṛa ur ilaq ara a d-ițwabdar gar-awen ulamma d abdar ;
M'ara ṛuḥeɣ ɣer yiwet n temdint, a d-tban tmanegt s tissit, tissas-agi ț-țeṛwiḥt i yimeqqranen n lmegtin. S wakka m'ara tebɣuɣuɣ iman-iw ilaq a d-tefkeḍ lweɛdat i Sidi Ṛebbi, s wakka aț-țesteɛfuɣ.
Axaṭer llan wid yeqqaṛen : tibṛatin n Bulus qeṛṛḥent, sɛant tissas lameɛna m'ara yili gar-aneɣ ur yesɛi lhiba ur yesɛi tissas di lehduṛ-is.
Yella wayen i d-ițeffɣen seg wedɣaɣ, d amuḍin neɣ d ameḥbus, ur d-yețțili ț-țamusni, ur ilaq ara ad yili d amuḍin neɣ d ameḥbus, ur d-yețțili ț-țaɛkumt,
